1. Question: Develop a page that has a link to download a sample PDF document. The link 
should open the PDF in a new tab.

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>PDF document</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h2>PDF document</h2>

    <a href="sample.pdf" target="_blank">click-me</a>

</body>
</html>

